{"word":"βέλτερος","slug":"βέλτερος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βέλτερος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Prob. from same Root as <el>βούλομαι.</el>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> and <a href='S:Superlative'>superl.</a> of <a href='S:ἀγαθός'><el>ἀγαθός</el></a>\n<p/><i>better, more excellent</i>, <el>βέλτερόν [ἐστι]</el> <i>it is better</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>; in <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/>"}]}